<h1>Bayesian Approach to Efficient Differential Allocation for Resampling-Based Significance Testing</h1>
<h2>Companion website to BMC Bioinformatics Jensen et al., 2009</h2>


<h3>R script for simulated GWAS data analysis</h3>

<ol>
<li><a href="shortcut.r">shortcut.r</a>, our shortcut implementation.
<li><a href="diff_alloc.r">diff_alloc.r</a>, our algorithm.
<li><a href="exp_shortcut.r">exp_shortcut.r</a>, top level R script for running the experiment using simulated GWAS data.
 <pre>
   Usage: R --no-save idx=[idx] < exp_shortcut.r  
   Use idx=0 to 29 to run 30 replicates in parallel.
 </pre> 
<li><a href="draw_exp_shortcut.r">draw_exp_shortcut.r</a>, R script for generating figures.
</ol>

